	<!DOCTYPE html>
	<html>
	  <head>
	    <title>Rental Stage</title>
	    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/bootstrap.css' />
	    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/index-custom.css' />
	  </head>
	  <body>

		  <% include ./partials/navbar %>


		<div class="bg"></div>
		<div class="jumbotron-1">
		  <h1>Welcome to rental stage</h1>
		  <p class="lead">property rental management </p>
		</div>
		<br>
		<br>
		<div class="container" style="padding-top: 50px">
	    <div class="row">

	            
	            <div class="col-md-4">
	                <div class="panel panel-default">
	                    <div class="panel-heading">
	                        <h4><i class="fa fa-fw fa-check"></i> Browse available propetry</h4>
	                    </div>
	                    <div class="panel-body">
	                        <p>You can browse for vailable  properties here. If you find an ideal place you can just drop a request and your details will be automatically set to the owner.</p>
	                          <a href="/property/property_feed" class="btn btn-default">Browse</a>
	                        
	                    </div>
	                </div>
	            </div>
	            <div class="col-md-4">
	                <div class="panel panel-default">
	                    <div class="panel-heading">
	                        <h4><i class="fa fa-fw fa-gift"></i> Advertise your property</h4>
	                    </div>
	                    <div class="panel-body">
	                        <p>If have a property for renting you can advertise here. Your data will be sent to potential buyers and they will request if intererested</p>
	                        <a href="/property/add_property" class="btn btn-default">Add property</a>
	                        
	                    </div>
	                </div>
	            </div>
	            <div class="col-md-4">
	                <div class="panel panel-default">
	                    <div class="panel-heading">
	                        <h4><i class="fa fa-fw fa-compass"></i> Manage your activities</h4>
	                    </div>
	                    <div class="panel-body">
	                        <p>You can organize all your activities very efficiently here. All your pending activities and related notifications are displayed for your convienenience.</p>
	                        <a href="users/dashbord" class="btn btn-default">Manage</a>
	                        

	                    </div>
	                </div>
	            </div>
	    </div>
	  </div>


	  

	  	<!-- jQuery (necessary for Bootstrap's JavaScript plugins) -->
	    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.12.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
	    <!-- Include all compiled plugins (below), or include individual files as needed -->
	    <script src="/javascripts/bootstrap.min.js"></script>


	    <script type="text/javascript">
	  	var jumboHeight = $('.jumbotron-1').outerHeight();
		function parallax(){
		    var scrolled = $(window).scrollTop();
		    $('.bg').css('height', (jumboHeight-scrolled) + "px");
		}

		$(window).scroll(function(e){
		    parallax();
		});
	  </script>


	  <% include ./partials/footer %>
	  </body>


	</html>
